<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="mernbackend/style.css">


    <style>
        .container {
            width: 800px;
            padding: 16px;
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            margin: 0 auto;
            margin-top: 50px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;

        }


        .form-group {
            width: 50%;
            padding: 1em;
        }

        form h2 {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .register-img {
            width: 50%;
            background-color: #017e7e;
        }

        input[type=text],
        input[type=password],
        input[type=email],
        input[type=tel] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        label {
            color: #017e7e;
        }

        input[type=radio] {
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .sec-1 {
            padding: 20px;
            /* border: 2px solid rebeccapurple; */
            color: #fff;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        .sec-1 button {
            color: #000;
            background-color: #fff;
        }

        .sec-1 h2 {
            color: #fff;
        }

        button {
            background-color: #017e7e;
            height: 45px;
            color: white;
            padding: 14px 20px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            width: 50%;
            font-weight: bold;
            /* margin: 0 0 0 10px; */
            border-radius: 31px;
        }




        button:hover {
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        .toggle-icon {
            position: absolute;
            top: 10px;
            right: 10px;
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #000;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .toggle-icon:hover {
            color: #fff;
        }

        .clearfix::after {
            content: "";
            clear: both;
            display: table;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #017e7e;
            font-family: sans-serif;

        }
    </style>



</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="register-img">
            <div class="sec-1">
                <h2>Information</h2>
                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Excepturi unde minima assumenda accusamus
                    sed dolorem, commodi sequi molestias ullam deleniti quam distinctio sapiente! Eum!</p>
                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Ipsam numquam, nemo repellendus hic,
                    praesentium culpa laudantium necessitatibus assumenda ducimus a doloremque temporibus neque maiores.
                </p>
                <button>Have an Account</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="registrationForm" class="form-group">
            <h2>Registration Form</h2>
            <form method="post">
                <label for="firstName"><b>First Name</b></label>
                <input type="text" placeholder="Enter your first name" name="firstName" required>

                <label for="lastName"><b>Last Name</b></label>
                <input type="text" placeholder="Enter your last name" name="lastName" required>

                <label for="email"><b>Email</b></label>
                <input type="email" placeholder="Enter your email" name="email" required>

                <label for="password"><b>Password</b></label>
                <input type="password" placeholder="Enter your password" name="password" required>

                <label for="confirmPassword"><b>Confirm Password</b></label>
                <input type="password" placeholder="Confirm your password" name="confirmPassword" required>

                <label for="gender"><b>Gender</b></label>
                <input type="radio" name="gender" value="male" checked> Male
                <input type="radio" name="gender" value="female"> Female

                <label for="phone"><b>Phone</b></label>
                <input type="tel" placeholder="Enter your phone number" name="phone" required>

                <label for="age"><b>Age</b></label>
                <input type="number" placeholder="Enter your age" name="age" required>

                <div class="clearfix">
                    <button type="submit">Register</button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>

    </div>





    </div>

